            <gco:CharacterString>
              Geographic coordinates in the occurrence_record.csv file are approximate. 
              Many locations were visually estimated from published maps and may contain 
              positional uncertainty ranging from several kilometers to regional-scale 
              imprecision. Some records lack precise coordinates due to limitations in 
              the original literature. These coordinates are included to provide general 
              spatial context and may be refined in future updates of the EMO Database. 
              Users should not treat these coordinates as precise sampling locations.
            </gco:CharacterString>
